Functional Requirements

The user must be able to create a profile 
Returning users must be able to log into profile 
The user must be able to edit profile information 
The user should be able to add and update their weight
The user could be able to set a weight goal 
The user should be able to track weight progress through a graph
The user must be able to start a new workout
The user must be able to cancel their workout 
The user should be able to upload a previous workout that they forgot to 
The user must be able to add different exercises to their workout
The user must be able to search for an exercise 
The user should be able to create a new exercise 
The user must be able to add the kg and number of reps for each exercise 
The user must be able to add a new set to an exercise 
The user must be able to save their workout
The user must be able to save a finished workout as a template they can re use 
The user must be able to select a pre existing template at the start of their workout 
The user must be able to view workout history 
The user should be able to view workout history in a calendar format 
The user could be able to take a fitness quiz that determines the best workout routine for them 
